{"tid":2130340,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我係地盤撚 林鄭我屌你老母","createTime":"2020-07-29T07:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T00:48:33.000Z","uid":13732,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2b26371f155494f63b731b7aaf7a46669494ff52","tid":2130340,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我做地盤。<br />\n今日晏晝放飯，我買咗碗牛腩河加啤酒。<br />\n「阿哥，無咗堂食喎。」粉麵店阿姐話。<br />\n「得喇！阿叔我單手拎住黎食！男人老狗，我唔驚熱既！」我。<br />\n阿姐冷笑咗一聲。<br />\n當我行出麵店，打算去附近公園坐低慢慢嘆。<br />\n我心諗，你班香港人真係唔捱得，外國人都係咁樣野餐咋！<br />\n點知&hellip;公園被紅膠帶封晒，唔講以為入面有命案發生。<br />\n算數！我行過去人少少嘅路邊食！<br />\n正當我打開個麵，諗起一個問題。<br />\n仆街&hellip;戶外口罩令，我一除低咗，咪犯法囉？！<br />\n唔緊要！我去商場啲後樓梯食！<br />\n好多廚房佬，晏晝落場都去嗰啲地方訓覺，仲有冷氣！不知幾爽！<br />\n點知，我一打開商場後門，見到已經有兩條友喺度食緊飯。<br />\n「室內限聚令兩人啊，過主啦！」其中一個話。<br />\n於是，我行晒成個區所有屋苑、商場&hellip;全部後樓梯都被人霸晒。<br />\n最後，我只好入去商場廁所，每格都有兩個人食緊飯！<br />\n我想食個飯啫，點解要咁對我喎？！<br />\n「你唔介意嘅入去食囉。」清潔廁所嘅阿叔，打開廁所放雜物嗰格畀我入去食飯。<br />\n我入到去，搬開啲雜物，坐咗喺廁所板。<br />\n突然間，一陣臭味傳過黎，隔籬廁格條仆街，食完飯即刻屙！<br />\n算數，我真係好肚餓&hellip;<br />\n我打開碗牛腩河，啲麵脹鳩晒！筷子夾極都夾唔起！<br />\n我飲咗一啖已經唔凍嘅啤酒，好苦，好澀<br />\n好似我人生一樣咁苦澀。<br />\n幾十歲人，我有咩苦未捱過？<br />\n我淨係唔想犯法，同埋食碗牛腩河啫&hellip;點解都咁囉啊？<br />\n嗰一刻，我忍唔住喊咗出嚟。<br />\n我唔敢抹眼淚，因為我啱啱先醒起，我唔記得洗手。"},{"pid":"172027d7722966cc376416aa6ec127355093d00f","tid":2130340,"uid":21170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"呢篇文好似喺一個舊登作者個page 睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c3323c9e1f80794afb8c43a3a44f5c1849e01b","tid":2130340,"uid":3287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"2020潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c492a80fcb88f850f1c7ca4145beaccd6289d719","tid":2130340,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"172027d7722966cc376416aa6ec127355093d00f","tid":2130340,"uid":21170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:01:18.000Z","msg":"呢篇文好似喺一個舊登作者個page 睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477bcb3979e2769087a9b1daa738dc42d042a8ac","tid":2130340,"uid":13732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"做人好苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cc0154acf04b22cb31fdb540ad15f8e847a2e4","tid":2130340,"uid":4957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"咪又係繼續返工"},{"pid":"58cf1470e7c7d03bef85e44b96904e10e2da1af8","tid":2130340,"uid":163255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"Quote返作者藍橘子啦"},{"pid":"4763b1a8c9662fcf172a3e5aa2ae96cc6b07fa87","tid":2130340,"uid":30293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:03:47.000Z","msg":"地盤佬表示wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工照開 飯照食 雞照叫"},{"pid":"3cbfd7b43411309e56fcd48796108d1d176152f6","tid":2130340,"uid":135040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:04:04.000Z","msg":"限定潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次見番可能幾年後"},{"pid":"5620b3ed54a868abecb63f57d97a9b11bb42ae18","tid":2130340,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9fe166c9619c635d9caeb850174fc92e6958b2f8","tid":2130340,"uid":21170,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"58cf1470e7c7d03bef85e44b96904e10e2da1af8","tid":2130340,"uid":163255,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"Quote返作者藍橘子啦"},"citedB